title: The Chinese president isn't visiting the UK for a debate about human rights, Chinese ambassador warns
text: The president of China is not visiting the UK for a “debate” about human rights issues, China’s ambassador to the UK has said. Liu Xiaoming said he did not think Labour leader Jeremy Corbyn would raise the issue of the country’s poor record
